ull wp-image-3826224" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-brandi-carlile@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-brandi-carlile@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-brandi-carlile@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-brandi-carlile@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-brandi-carlile@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-brandi-carlile@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-brandi-carlile@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3826224" class="wp-caption-text">埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）和布兰迪·卡莱尔（Brandi Carlile）在2025年金球奖（Golden Globes）举行。图片来源：Rich Polk/GG2025/Penske Media通过Get Images</figcaption></figure><p> “谁相信天使？”定于4月4日通过Island EMI发行，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andrew-watt">安德鲁·瓦特（Andrew Watt）</a>和约翰（John）的长期歌曲创作伙伴伯尼·陶彭（Bernie Taupin）的合作。</p><p>它是传奇艺术家2021专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/elton-john-the-lockdown-sessions-review-3073859">《 The Lockdown Sessions》</a>的后续作品，还包括2025年以<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>为主导的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-elton-john-and-brandi-carlile-new-song-never-too-late-written-for-upcoming-documentary-3813101">“ Never Tor Toot Toot Toothe”</a> ，该歌曲是为<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/elton-john-never-too-late-review-dodger-stadium-3821275">迪士尼+同名纪录片</a>创建的。<a href="https://eltonjohn.lnk.to/WBIAAlbum">访问此处进行预订。</a></p><p>在LP中，两者得到了标志性音乐家的支持，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">红辣椒</a>的鼓手Chad Smith，Pino Palladino（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nine-inch-nails">九英寸指甲</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gary-numan">Gary Numan</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-gilmour">David Gilmour</a> ）和Josh Klinghoffer（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beck">Beck</a> ）。</p><p>在其他新闻中，上个月透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-told-brandi-carlile-to-fuck-off-and-smashed-his-ipad-during-tense-duets-album-sessions-3836025">“火箭”的杀手砸了他的iPad，并告诉卡莱尔在制作专辑中“滚蛋”</a> ，此后，他继续<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-praises-extraordinary-kneecap-i-love-everything-about-them-3843420">为Kneecap分享赞美，称他们为“非凡”。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-and-brandi-carliles-upcoming-london-palladium-show-is-being-turned-into-a-tv-special-3847366">埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）和布兰迪·卡利尔（Brandi Carlile）即将举行的伦敦钯节（London Palladium Show）正在</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现在电视节目中。</p> ;
